                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-text mb-4">
                        Complete House Construction
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-brand-text-light mb-6">
                        Full-service residential construction from foundation to
                        finishing. We handle every aspect of your dream home
                        with precision and care.
                    </p>
                    <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-brand-text-light">
                        <li class="flex items-center">
                            <svg
                                class="w-4 h-4 text-brand-cyan mr-2 flex-shrink-0"
                                fill="currentColor"
